<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her pfleger, <add>uns hat</add> unser
                                <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der <expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<add>czu wissen getan, wie er nehst mit euch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lassen</expan> hab</add>, waz
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> euch von den, die den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ir habe und
                                <expan>kauffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> geleyte <add>umb</add> euch aufgehalten
                        und <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, werde, daz ir uns die fürbaz czu wissen tun
                        süllet. Darümb so senden wir czu euch Hansen <expan>Swob<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener,
                            <expan>czeig<ex>er</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>, und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob euch darümb
                                <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex>ley</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz ir uns die bey
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener wissen lasset, und waz auch
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> unser dyener darümb czu disem mal an
                        euch werb von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, daz ir im des
                                <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und darynn
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tun wöllet. Als etc. Das wöllen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Viti. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>Rab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, amptman zu Plawen
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
